NAME
    Search::Elasticsearch::Client::2_0::Async - Thin async client with full
    support for Elasticsearch 2.x APIs

VERSION
    version 5.02

DESCRIPTION
    The Search::Elasticsearch::Client::2_0::Async package provides a client
    compatible with Elasticsearch 2.x. It should be used in conjunction with
    Search::Elasticsearch::Async as follows:

        $e = Search::Elasticsearch::Async->new(
            client => "2_0::Direct"
        );

    See Search::Elasticsearch::Client::2_0::Direct for documentation about
    how to use the client itself.

